Description :
        As spatial nodes descend, secret realms and abyssal dungeons emerge one after another, unleashing hordes of monsters and demonic forces in a wild frenzy! The only way to survive and reach the pinnacle of the world is to become a professional, grow stronger through battle!On the day of awakening, Su Chen became the first person in history with no profession. Amid the mockery of countless others, he silently activated his system, breaking all the rules and stunning everyone!
